    "title": "Career Opportunity Teacher at Gradeup",
    "description": "Gradeup invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Teacher at our Indore location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Gradeup:\nGradeup is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gradeup!",
